core.planner
Class Method

java.lang.Object
  core.planner.Method
All Implemented Interfaces:
Standardizable, java.lang.Cloneable
public final class Method
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, Standardizable

The Method class implements a method. The class represents a method defined in the planning domain. A method have the form: (:method h C1 T1 C2 T2 ... Cn Tn).
